WEBVTT

00:00:58.999 --> 00:01:02.696
na utafiti nilioona
utakushangaza:

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:06.330
kila mtu unaempenda ana
nafasi asilimia 100 ya kufa.

00:01:06.354 --> 00:01:08.950
(Kicheko)

00:01:08.974 --> 00:01:10.545
Na ndio maana ukaja TED.

00:01:10.569 --> 00:01:12.631
(Kicheko)

00:01:12.655 --> 00:01:15.967
(Makofi)

00:01:16.292 --> 00:01:18.022
Tangu hasara yote ilivyonitokea,

00:01:18.046 --> 00:01:22.339
nimefanya kazi kuongelea kuhusu kifo na
hasara,

00:01:22.363 --> 00:01:24.783
sio yangu tu,
kwa sababu ni rahisi kukumbuka,

00:01:24.807 --> 00:01:28.853
lakini hasara na mikasa
ambayo watu wengine wamepitia.

00:01:28.877 --> 00:01:31.216
Ni sehemu, naweza kusema.